Dependencies
============

hachoir-metadata:
 * hachoir-core 1.3
 * hachoir-parser 1.3

hachoir-metadata-gtk:
 * pygtk (Debian package: python-gtk2)

hachoir-metadata-qt:
 * PyQt4

To compile hachoir_metadata/qt/dialog.ui, you need pyuic4 which is part of
PyQt4 development tools.


Install
=======

Run the follow command as root: ::

    ./setup.py install

